TODO Command line interface

Debugger:
A visual debugger written using FLTK. This is currently work in progress.
Features:
* memory view
* disassembly
* stepping
* reverse stepping
TODO:
* gui layout
* loading from file
* break points
* watch memory/cpu state


Building the tools:
Dependencies: scons, fltk
Run scons in the project's root directory.

